    <item>
      <title>软银支持的 Oyo 计划发行 4.5 亿美元债券进行再融资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/softbank-backed-oyo-eyes-450-million-bond-sale-for-refinancing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位知情人士透露，Oyo Hotels 正在商谈通过美元债券筹集最多 4.5 亿美元资金，这家曾经风光无限的印度初创公司因推迟上市而寻求取代现有的高成本贷款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/softbank-backed-oyo-eyes-450-million-bond-sale-for-refinancing</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 09:45:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>增长前景阴云笼罩，外国对华投资下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/foreign-investment-in-china-falls-with-cloud-over-growth-outlook</link>
      <description><![CDATA[与去年同期相比，3月份流入中国的外国投资连续第三个月放缓，突显出北京方面难以吸引更多海外资金来提振经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/foreign-investment-in-china-falls-with-cloud-over-growth-outlook</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 09:37:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>花旗：市场可能对中东紧张局势反应过度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-19/markets-could-be-overreacting-to-mideast-tension-citi-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[花旗集团全球首席经济学家内森·希茨(Nathan Sheets)表示，市场往往对地缘政治事件“最初反应过度”，例如两名美国官员关于以色列对伊朗发动袭击的报道。 “这种过度反应反映了第一次爆发时的不确定性溢价，但通常这些事件最终的破坏性没有我们担心的那么大，”希茨告诉彭博电视台。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-19/markets-could-be-overreacting-to-mideast-tension-citi-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 09:29:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中东冲突扰乱市场，亚洲加强货币防御</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/asia-steps-up-currency-defense-as-mideast-strife-roils-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着亚洲对抗美元复苏的斗争面临来自中东武装冲突报道的新挑战，从雅加达到首尔的各国央行都加强了对其货币的保护。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/asia-steps-up-currency-defense-as-mideast-strife-roils-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 09:23:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马来西亚资产抵御中东担忧引发的抛售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/malaysian-assets-defy-selloff-spurred-by-middle-east-concerns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于围绕国家经济前景的乐观情绪以及当地基金支持的猜测，马来西亚资产周五顶住了新兴市场的广泛抛售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/malaysian-assets-defy-selloff-spurred-by-middle-east-concerns</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 09:13:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>北美市场表现超出预期，可可创下新纪录</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/cocoa-hits-new-record-as-north-america-grinds-defy-expectation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管全球供应紧缩且价格创纪录，但由于巧克力工厂的加工速度仍保持不变，纽约的可可期货创下了新纪录。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/cocoa-hits-new-record-as-north-america-grinds-defy-expectation</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 09:12:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>《泰晤士报》称，泰晤士水务公司寻求将水费提高 56%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/thames-water-resubmits-plan-seeking-56-bills-rise-times</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《泰晤士报》报道，泰晤士水务公司正寻求将客户账单增加 56%，为其五年支出计划提供资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/thames-water-resubmits-plan-seeking-56-bills-rise-times</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 08:24:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于市场考虑打击伊朗，欧洲天然气回吐涨幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/european-gas-steadies-as-market-weighs-strike-on-iran</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于伊朗似乎淡化了据报道的以色列袭击的影响以及德黑兰立即做出反应的风险，欧洲天然气价格回吐涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/european-gas-steadies-as-market-weighs-strike-on-iran</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 07:41:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
